org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.lazybinary

Class LazyBinarySerDe2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.AbstractSerDe
      • org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.lazybinary.LazyBinarySerDe
        • org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.lazybinary.LazyBinarySerDe2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Deserializer, Serializer

    public class LazyBinarySerDe2
extends LazyBinarySerDe
    Subclass of LazyBinarySerDe with faster serialization, initializing a serializer based on the row columns rather than checking the ObjectInspector category/primitiveType for every value. This appears to be around 3x faster than the LazyBinarSerDe serialization.
